  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Q’oñi jall’aspi, chin jallp’aspi Dios Tatawan./
 /P'unchay jamuni, tutas jamuni Dios Tatawan./
 
[V2]
 /Mayús pasani, lomas pasani Dios Tatawan./
 /Maná munanki purikuytaqa Dios Tatawan?/
 
[V3]
 /Imaspis kachun, kawsay munani Dios Tatawan./
 /Wañunaykama noqa purisaj Dios Tatawan./
 
[V4]
 /Nanayniykipi, waqayniykipi Dios Tatawan./
 /Maná munanki takipuytaqa Dios Tatapaj?/
 
</lyrics></song>